Requirements : use arrow keys from keyboard as input to the game to move the snake around
Condition : snake has to eat a food to grow to a length of one.
	snake dies if the player hits the boundray or hits itself
Scores : scores are calculated inaccordance to the number of food being ate
	highscores are stored seperatly
level : speed of the snake moving around the screen is gradually increased with the number of food being had.
	when the snake grows to the maximum of the screen size, new screen in opened with the snake being small and the scores are carried over.
